description: The Indian government is evaluating potential changes to GST rates to address imbalances, including the inverted duty structure. description: Officials in the Ministry of Finance are discussing proposals to reduce taxes for high-spending consumers. Individuals earning between 500,000 rupees ($5,987) and 1.5 million rupees, currently taxed at rates from 5% to 20%, may benefit from this move. The introduction of a new tax slab is also under consideration. The details are still being finalized, with a decision expected near the budget announcement in July, pending approval from the PMO. description: In other wedding news, ahead of Sonakshi and Zaheer's wedding, a fun-filled picture of Zaheer enjoying his bachelor party with close friends surfaced online. Sonakshi was also seen having a blast with her girl gang, including Huma Qureshi, at her bachelorette party.
title: Shatrughan Sinha poses with soon to be son-in-law Zaheer: Watch

description: A United Airlines flight bound for Denver returned to Bradley International Airport in Hartford, Connecticut, after a piece of the engine's sound-dampening outer liner fell off during takeoff.  The crew of the Airbus A320 heard an "abnormal noise" shortly after departure and decided to turn back, according to the Federal Aviation Administration (FAA).
title: United Airlines jet turns back after engine piece falls off

description: Pat Cummins took a hat-trick against Bangladesh in their T20 World Cup Super 8 clash at Antigua on Friday. Cummins, Australia's Test and ODI captain, dismissed Mahmudullah, Mahedi Hasan, Towhid Hridoy to become the fourth Australian to take a hat-trick in T20Is. Cummins became only the second Aussie, after Brett Lee, to take a hat-trick in the T20 World Cup.
title: Watch: Pat Cummins registers first hat-trick of T20 WC 2024

description: Jasprit Bumrah showcased his exceptional skills in the T20 World Cup, demonstrating his importance to India's success. With only seven runs in four overs and three wickets, Bumrah helped India start their Super Eight stage with a commanding victory over Afghanistan. India bowlers led by Bumrah bowled out Afghanistan for 134, registering a 47-run win.
title: 'Important to use him smartly': Rohit praises Bumrah's class act

description: Govindaraj alias Kannukutti, the main suspect in the Kallakurichi hooch tragedy, was arrested for illegal sale of liquor bottles. He was previously detained under the Goondas Act. Now, along with his wife Vijaya and another person Thamodhiran, he has been arrested for the death of about 40 people at Karunapuram in Kallakurichi.
title: Tamil Nadu hooch tragedy: Main suspect was held 10 days ago but ...

description: Sandalwood actor Darshan's girlfriend Pavithra Gowda instigated and conspired the murder of Chitradurga resident Renukaswamy S, as per the prosecution in a magistrate court. The actor used aides to execute the crime and dispose of the body, with Pavithra identified as the prime conspirator.
title: Renukaswamy murder: 'Pavithra instigator, Darshan executor'

description: Ricky Ponting presented Pat Cummins with the ICC Men's International Cricketer of the Year 2023 award in a ceremony. Ponting handed over the trophy to Cummins before the T20 World Cup Super 8 clash between Australia and Bangladesh in Antigua. Apart from leading Australia to the ODI World Cup title, Cummins also won the World Test Championship title and also retained the urn with a drawn Ashes series in England.
title: Watch: Pat Cummins handed over Sir Garfield Sobers trophy

description: An inspection report on the Rudraprayag accident highlighted fraud suspicions in the driver's fee payment and safety lapses. The incident involved a Tempo Traveller plunging into the Alaknanda river, leading to 15 fatalities. Recommendations for enhanced safety measures were proposed to prevent similar tragedies in the future.
title: Probe into Uttarakhand crash that killed 15 reveals driving test fraud

description: Fit and Flex, Culver Max Entertainment, and Pathik Patel face issues with Sony Pictures Networks over contractual violations and social media account deactivation in Shark Tank India update.
title: Shark Tank India 3's snacking start-up owner sends legal notice to channel

description: India defeated Afghanistan by 47 runs in the T20 World Cup Super Eights match. Jasprit Bumrah's outstanding performance led to Afghanistan being bowled out for 134 while chasing 182. Former cricketer Mohammad Kaif praised Bumrah's skills and impact on the game. On a slow-paced Barbados wicket, Bumrah took three wickets for just seven runs in his four-over spell.
title: 'Bumrah ke paas aisi kala hai...': Ex-cricketer lauds India pacer
